name: Dynamic Active U.S. Investment Grade Corporate Bond ETF
longDescription: To achieve its investment objectives, DXBU will invest primarily in U.S. dollar denominated investment grade corporate bonds such that the overall weighted average credit rating of the ETF will remain investment grade. DXBU seeks to provide income and longterm capital appreciation.
